
Which of the following is true of a Relational Database? (Select all that apply to Relational Databases, do NOT select things associated with Transactional Databases)


Information is not stored in a way that’s conducive to querying and analysis.


Used to optimize querying data, making it easy and intuitive to access the data(selected)

